<%= form_with model: [:admin, @test], local: true do |form| %>
  <%= render 'shared/errors', resource: @test %>

  <p>
    <%= form.label :title %><br>
    <%= form.text_field :title, id: :test_title %>
  </p>

  <p>
    <%= form.label :level %><br>
    <%= form.number_field :level, id: :test_level %>
  </p>

  <p>
    <%= form.label :category_id %><br>
    <%= form.collection_select :category_id, Category.all, :id, :title, prompt: true %>
  </p>

If the test should have a timer, enter minutes and seconds for the timer:
  <div class='form-row'>
    <p>
      <%= form.number_field :minutes, id: :minutes, placeholder: 'minutes', min: 0, max: 59 %>
    </p>

    <p>
      <%= form.number_field :seconds, id: :seconds, placeholder: 'seconds', min: 0, max: 59 %>
    </p>
  </div>

  <p><%= form.submit %></p>
<% end %>
